collectible.name: Hip Hop Heads Microphone
collectible.description: Commemorative (wearable) collectible from the Hip Hop Heads Concert held on 12/22/2021. Hip Hop Heads (HHH) is Louie C Rhymes official debut album delivered through 5,000 uniquely generated NFTs with a twist; each one contains part of the album as an audio component with its own rarity! IT'S LOUIE BABY!
